description: Folks of Phoenix, if you’re feeling quite thirsty, you’re in for a treat. Nice cool beverages and frozen sweets are this trusty tricycle’s specialty. You can catch Special Teas pedaling around the streets of Phoenix, peddling out water, juice, teas, fruit bars, and classic popsicles like Fudge Pops and Bomb Pops, all for your refreshment needs. For maximum quali-tea of life, make it a priori-tea to check out Special Teas.
name: Special Teas
